Wendy!

76
00:06:30,790 --> 00:06:31,560
Đưa cho tôi!

77
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,260
John!

78
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:33,460
Wendy!

79
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:34,760
Lê cái mông anh đến đây mau!

80
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,530
John!

81
00:06:36,530 --> 00:06:37,300
Wendy!

82
